;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;">Ryan wants to dramatically cut pr=
ograms for the poor<br>
<br>
</span></b><span style=3D"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roma=
n&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;">Ryan's entitlement cuts aren't where his budgets=
