<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Ti=
mes New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;">These are truly massive cuts that wo=
uld likely throw millions of Americans into poverty. And they're actually s=
omewhat milder than his early proposals, which envisioned
<span style=3D"color:#1F497D"><a href=3D"http://www.cbpp.org/research/the-r=
yan-budgets-radical-priorities">eliminating Medicaid almost entirely</a>
