<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Ti=
mes New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Ti=
mes New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;">Ryan has since tried to rebrand hims=
elf as a compassionate conservative who cares about poverty, unveiling
<span style=3D"color:#1F497D">a <a href=3D"http://www.vox.com/cards/paul-ry=
an-poverty/what-is-paul-ryans-plan-to-expand-the-eitc">
much-touted poverty plan</a> </span>in 2014 and holding a widely publicized=
 &quot;<span style=3D"color:#1F497D"><a href=3D"http://www.cbpp.org/poverty=
-and-inequality/gop-poverty-forum-its-high-notes-and-low-notes">poverty for=
um</a></span>&quot; for the Republican presidential
 contenders this year.<span style=3D"color:#1F497D"><o:p></o:p></span></spa=
n></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Ti=
mes New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;color:#1F497D"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></spa=
n></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Ti=
mes New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;">But this has changed precious little=
 of the substance of his views on poverty. He has a proposal to expand the =
earned income tax credit for childless workers and non-custodial
 parents, but he would pay for it by cutting other safety net programs, inc=
luding
<span style=3D"color:#1F497D"><a href=3D"http://www.cbpp.org/blog/ryan-adds=
-momentum-to-expanding-eitc-for-childless-workers">denying millions of chil=
dren of undocumented immigrants access</a>
</span>to the child tax credit (even though many of those children are US c=
itizens).<o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Ti=
mes New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Ti=
mes New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;">While his plan is basically identica=
l to President Obama's EITC expansion proposal,
<span style=3D"color:#1F497D"><a href=3D"http://www.vox.com/2016/1/12/10758=
